## Comments

### Business Rules
- Comments can only be posted on **Published** articles
- Users can only edit or delete **their own** comments
- Admin can delete any comment
- Comment order: chronological (oldest first)
- No nesting/threading in MVP

```typescript
// src/services/comment.service.ts
async addComment(articleId: string, authorId: string, body: string): Promise<Comment> {
  const article = await articleRepository.findById(articleId);
  if (!article || article.status !== 'Published') {
    throw new AppError('Cannot comment on this article', 403);
  }
  return commentRepository.create({ articleId, authorId, body });
}

async editComment(commentId: string, userId: string, body: string): Promise<Comment> {
  const comment = await commentRepository.findById(commentId);
  if (!comment) throw new AppError('Comment not found', 404);
  if (comment.authorId !== userId) throw new AppError('Not authorized', 403);
  return commentRepository.update(commentId, { body });
}
```

